Grenade based algae
This is basically just algae from the tutorial
However I include it because I think the lower ranks benefit from
more sides. And frankly, it doesn't do all that bad, for what it is.

#color 992
#type Grenade Algae
#hardware
	processor 1
	solar-cells .3
	constructor .3
	energy 100 0
	armor 100
	grenades 30 17 40
	robot-sensor 17
#code
do
	autoconstruct
	grenades-reload-time periodic-robot-sensor if
		robot-found if
			robot-position robot-velocity lead-grenade
		then
	then
forever
#end
